text:
Mountains are quite 
The springs are empty 
The trees have dried up
The winds are motionless
The ice is melting
The nights have been more scary 
The desert have grown more
The leaves are dry
The sky is red
Moon is decreasing 
Sun is in anger 
Something is missing
